2009年11月，柏利獲得生涯第一座金手套獎，另外還獲得了菲爾丁聖經獎（Fielding Bible Award）<ref>{{cite web|title=The 2009 Awards |url=http://www.billjamesonline.net/fieldingbible/the-2009-winners.asp |publisher=The Fielding Bible |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101105001529/http://www.billjamesonline.net/fieldingbible/the-2009-winners.asp |archive-date=2010-11-05 |access-date=2010-11-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，顯示其防守能力已受到專家一致性的肯定。柏利在2009年球季的成績為：13勝10負，防禦率3.84，連續第九季至少投滿200局。

2010年4月5日，柏利於球季開幕戰中主投，五局上半一個精彩的守備<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n_m3qy2O7bA |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-08-14 |archive-date=2021-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419120553/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n_m3qy2O7bA |dead-url=no }}</ref>，轟動了全美體壇，柏利也順利拿下了連續第二年的金手套獎以及防守聖經獎<ref name=gleeman>{{cite news |title=Yadier Molina leads fifth annual "Fielding Bible Awards" |first=Aaron |last=Gleeman |url=http://hardballtalk.nbcsports.com/2010/11/01/yadier-molina-leads-fifth-annual-fielding-bible-awards/ |work=NBCSports.com |date=2010-11-01 |access-date=2010-11-11 |quote=For those of us who have come to more or less ignore Gold Glove awards as a meaningful way to measure defensive excellence, the fifth annual Fielding Bible Awards were announced today. |archive-date=2010-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101103232951/http://hardballtalk.nbcsports.com/2010/11/01/yadier-molina-leads-fifth-annual-fielding-bible-awards/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{notetag|迄此，柏利成為史上第一位至少投出二場無安打比賽，又得到至少二座金手套獎的選手。}}。8月3日，柏利對底特律老虎取勝，這是球季的第十勝，也保證了個人連續第十個球季皆有雙位數勝投入手。柏利在2010年球季的成績結算為13勝13負、防禦率4.28，並再一次達標200局以上的投球貢獻（連續第十季）。

2011年球季，柏利的表現依舊，通算13勝9負、防禦率3.59，連續第十一年至少投滿200局，也是連續第三年拿到金手套獎和防守聖經獎<ref>{{cite web |title=The 2011 Awards |url=http://fieldingbible.com/the-winners.asp |publisher=The Fielding Bible |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111102034331/http://www.fieldingbible.com/the-winners.asp |archive-date=2011-11-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在離開芝加哥之前，他留下了總計161勝119負，平均防禦率3.83的成績，一共四次入選明星賽<ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/b/buehrma01.shtml |title=Mark Buehrle Stats {{!}} Baseball-Reference.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-02-07 |archive-date=2021-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420024543/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/b/buehrma01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 邁阿密馬林魚 ====
2011年12月7日，柏利同意了[[邁阿密馬林魚|邁阿密馬林魚]]隊所開的四年58,000,000美金合約<ref>{{cite news|last=Frisaro|first=Joe|title=Buehrle agrees to four-year deal with Marlins|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20111207&content_id=26121258&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|access-date=2011-12-07|newspaper=MLB.com|date=2011-12-07|archive-date=2014-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427013505/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20111207&content_id=26121258&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月5日是柏利首披馬林魚制服的先發，惜並未取勝<ref>{{cite web|title=Miami Marlins vs. Cincinnati Reds recap|url=http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/boxscore?gameId=320405117|access-date=2021-02-07|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064846/http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/boxscore?gameId=320405117|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月18日，柏利對[[芝加哥小熊|芝加哥小熊]]投出8局失1分的優異成績，拿下球季第一勝，也是代表馬林魚隊的第一勝。5月5日，柏利對[[聖地牙哥教士|聖地牙哥教士]]投出9局失1分完投勝。柏利在2011年球季的成績為13勝13負、防禦率3.74、125次，並連續第十二年投滿至少200局，也連續第四年拿到金手套獎和防守聖經獎<ref>{{cite web|title=The 2012 Awards |date=2012-10-25 |url=http://www.actasports.com/stats_detail/?StatId=345 |publisher=ACTA Sports |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121027035418/http://www.actasports.com/stats_detail/?StatId=345 |archive-date=2012-10-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

==== 多倫多藍鳥 ====
2012年11月19日，柏利和[[喬許·詹森|喬許·強森]]、[[何塞·雷耶斯|荷西·雷耶斯]]等幾名球員一同被交易至[[多倫多藍鳥|多倫多藍鳥]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=409853|title=MLB approves mega-deal between Blue Jays and Marlins|work=TSN.ca|date=2012-11-19|access-date=2012-11-19|archive-date=2012-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121127174426/http://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=409853|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他以第三號先發的身分展開球季<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130205&content_id=41426288&notebook_id=41426816&vkey=notebook_tor&c_id=tor|title=Blue Jays set rotation around No. 1 Dickey|last=Toman|first=Chris|website=MLB.com|date=2013-02-05|access-date=2013-02-05|archive-date=2013-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102075427/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130205&content_id=41426288&notebook_id=41426816&vkey=notebook_tor&c_id=tor|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{notetag|該年藍鳥的頭牌先發為蝴蝶球投手[[R·A·迪奇|R·A·迪奇]]。}}。2013年7月25日，柏利對休士頓太空人投出了完投完封勝，該場勝利是藍鳥的第八十一勝，使他們得以中止連續7季勝少敗多的局面<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=428465|title=Buehrle helps Blue Jays beat Astros to end losing streak|publisher=TSN.ca|date=2013-07-25|access-date=2013-07-25|archive-date=2014-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140105094815/http://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=428465|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

8月25日，柏利再次對太空人取勝，這是他個人的第十勝，也意味著他連續第十三年取得雙位數勝投。9月21日，他在對陣波士頓紅襪的比賽中跨越球季200局里程碑，此亦是連續13季的成就。柏利的2013年球季成績為12勝10負、防禦率4.15、139次奪三振、200.2局投球。可惜的是，他在防守金手套獎的競爭上負於隊友[[R·A·迪奇|R·A·迪奇]]。

2014年開季的柏利特別犀利，連續拿下4勝之外，期間的平均防禦率僅有0.69，使他獲選4月的美聯最佳球員（與隊友[[梅基·卡布瑞拉|梅基·卡布瑞拉]]共同獲選）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://toronto.bluejays.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140501&content_id=73968734&c_id=tor&vkey=pr_tor|title=Mark Buehrle & Melky Cabrera named Honda Co-Player Of The Month|work=MLB.com|date=2014-05-01|access-date=2014-05-01|archive-date=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502144933/http://toronto.bluejays.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140501&content_id=73968734&c_id=tor&vkey=pr_tor|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月7日，柏利面對費城費城人再次取勝，不僅是個人的球季第六勝，更是當季大聯盟最快達標的投手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=451556|title=Buehrle gets league leading sixth win as Jays rout Phillies|work=TSN.ca|date=2014-05-07|access-date=2014-05-07|archive-date=2014-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140508062348/http://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=451556|dead-url=no}}</ref>。繼續在5月12日（洛杉磯天使）、5月17日（德州遊騎兵）取勝之後，他已累積7勝。5月22日，藍鳥前往波士頓踢館，柏利獲得球季第八勝（領先全大聯盟），氣勢如虹的藍鳥亦在客場橫掃了紅襪。挾此鴻運，柏利在5月27日再次拿下勝投，為個人第9勝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_05_27_tbamlb_tormlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=tor|title=Toronto rides long ball to eighth straight victory|last=Chisholm|first=Gregor|work=MLB.com|date=2014-05-27|access-date=2014-05-27|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045404/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_05_27_tbamlb_tormlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=tor|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

6月1日，柏利取得球季個人第十勝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_06_01_kcamlb_tormlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=tor|title=Buehrle baffles Royals for MLB-best 10th win|last=Ross|first=Jamie|work=MLB.com|date=2014-06-01|access-date=2014-06-01|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230453/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_06_01_kcamlb_tormlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=tor|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此後柏利的表現有所下滑，球季剩餘的19場先發中，他僅取得2勝9負的成績。9月24日，他再次跨越球季200局投球的門檻，亦是個人生涯連續14年達陣<ref name="14 seasons">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_09_24_seamlb_tormlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=tor|title=Buehrle hits 200 IP for 14th straight year in win|last=Chisholm|first=Gregor|work=MLB.com|date=2014-09-24|access-date=2014-09-24|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041949/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_09_24_seamlb_tormlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=tor|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年球季，柏利被定位為藍鳥第四號先發。4月10日，他對[[金鶯|金鶯]]隊取得勝利，這是他的生涯第二百勝{{notetag|現役選手中，僅[[巴特羅·柯隆|巴特羅·柯隆]]、[[:en:Tim_Hudson|:en:Tim Hudson]]以及[[卡斯坦·查爾斯·沙巴西亞|C·C·沙巴西亞]]有此成就。}}。5月29日，柏利以完投勝擊敗明尼蘇達雙城<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.torontosun.com/2015/05/29/buehrle-overcomes-rough-first-to-post-complete-game-in-jays-win|title=Buehrle overcomes ugly first to post complete game in Jays win|last=Fidlin|first=Ken|work=torontosun.com|date=2015-05-29|access-date=2015-06-03|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127185414/https://torontosun.com/2015/05/29/buehrle-overcomes-rough-first-to-post-complete-game-in-jays-win|dead-url=no}}</ref>，續於次一場先發中以精簡的93球擊敗華盛頓國民<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/buehrle-throws-cg-shutout-as-blue-jays-rout-nats/|title=Buehrle throws CG shutout as Blue Jays rout Nats|work=Sportsnet|date=2015-06-03|access-date=2015-06-03|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123171941/https://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/buehrle-throws-cg-shutout-as-blue-jays-rout-nats/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月6日，他再次面對雙城取勝，這是其生涯面對雙城的第卅勝，使他達成一項特殊紀錄：1961年以來，對單一球隊成功取得30勝或以上<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/141708996|title=Stats of the Day: Buehrle has Twins' number|last=Schlueter|first=Roger|work=MLB.com|date=2015-08-07|access-date=2015-08-07|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081616/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/141708996|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{notetag|此項紀錄僅20人達成，柏利為第廿一位。}}）。10月2日，柏利登板面對坦帕灣光芒，取得球季個人第十五勝。由於他被預期可能被排除在季後賽名單外，一般認為他將會在隔天的比賽中再次登場，並嘗試負擔2局的投球工作，以期能延續球季200局投球的紀錄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.nbcsports.com/2015/10/03/report-mark-buehrle-to-throw-two-innings-on-sunday-then-retire/|title=Report: Mark Buehrle to throw two innings on Sunday, then retire|last=Baer|first=Bill|work=mlb.nbcsports.com|date=2015-10-03|access-date=2015-10-03|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214150420/https://mlb.nbcsports.com/2015/10/03/report-mark-buehrle-to-throw-two-innings-on-sunday-then-retire/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而柏利僅完成了2/3局的投球便被替換離場，主因是隊友在守備上的失誤導致伯利上場的時候失掉大量非自責分數。在賽後所公布的季後賽名單中，未有柏利的參與，但他向記者表示自己尚未決定退休與否<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/13808028/mark-buehrle-toronto-blue-jays-fails-bid-pitch-200-innings|title=Mark Buehrle fails to notch 15th straight season of 200 innings pitched|work=espn.go.com|date=2015-10-04|access-date=2015-10-05|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303182102/http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/13808028/mark-buehrle-toronto-blue-jays-fails-bid-pitch-200-innings|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

最終，柏利的2015年球季成績為15勝8負、防禦率3.81、91次奪三振<ref name="BR">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/b/buehrma01.shtml|title=Mark Buehrle Statistics and History|work=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2015-10-05|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420024543/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/b/buehrma01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{notetag|他的每九局奪三振數（4.12）是當年全大聯盟最低的，此外他的被擊球率（89.1%）則領先全大聯盟。這意味著他的球威不足，打者能更容易地掌握他的球路，卻沒有影響他的整體表現，此一現象引起了各界的討論<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=5&season=2015&month=0&season1=2015&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=8,d |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2015 » Pitchers » Plate Discipline Statistics {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-02-07 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812133447/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=5&season=2015&month=0&season1=2015&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=8,d |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2015&month=0&season1=2015&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=9,a |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2015 » Pitchers » Dashboard {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-02-07 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812133441/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2015&month=0&season1=2015&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=9,a |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}。10月29日，柏利入選了防守金手套獎的最終名單<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/155895822/gold-glove-award-finalists-announced|title=Finalists for Gold Gloves unveiled|work=MLB.com|date=2015-10-29|access-date=2015-10-29|archive-date=2017-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170708073932/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/155895822/gold-glove-award-finalists-announced/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

柏利在多倫多時期的成績結算為40勝28負、平均防禦率3.79，並入選明星賽一次。2015年賽季結束後也未繼續登板投球，以低調的方式退休。

